HEADWORD: Arithmetical
<hw>Ar`ith*met"ic*al</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to arithmetic; according to the rules or method of
arithmetic.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

